width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Project data: Hoeveel fietsen worden er in Rotterdam gestolen?","date":"2017-04-18","category":"projects"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/Project-data-hoeveel-gestolen-fietsen-in-Rotterdam/"}}